# 7: Modules
#############

# FvwmScript
#
# FvwmScript is a module that allows one to write custom desktop
# widgets and various other tools. This config uses two FvwmScripts.
#   - DateTime - uses the output of "date" to display the date/time
#     on the RightPanel.
#   - Quit - This is a popup that asks for quit confirmation before
#     quitting fvwm.
DestroyModuleConfig FvwmScript:*
*FvwmScript: DefaultColorset 10

# FvwmButtons
#
# Note - To use the system tray you must have "stalonetray" installed.
DestroyModuleConfig HorizontalPanel:*
*HorizontalPanel: Geometry $[vp.width]x$[infostore.horizontal_panel_height]+0+0
*HorizontalPanel: Colorset 10
*HorizontalPanel: Rows $[infostore.horizontal_panel_height]
*HorizontalPanel: Columns $[vp.width]
*HorizontalPanel: (25x20, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 11, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*HorizontalPanel: (25x20, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*HorizontalPanel: (25x20, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*HorizontalPanel: (25x20, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*HorizontalPanel: (194x1-0+0, Container)
*HorizontalPanel: (120x45, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-DateTime', Frame 0)
*HorizontalPanel: (End)

## Workspace Indicator
DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPager: *
AddToFunc StartFunction
+ I Module FvwmPager *
*FvwmPager: font none
*FvwmPager: Colorset * 1
*FvwmPager: HilightColorset * 15
*FvwmPager: WindowColorsets 13 14
*FvwmPager: SolidSeparators
*FvwmPager: UseSkipList
*FvwmPager: Geometry 56x126+12-12
*FvwmPager: WindowBorderWidth 2
*FvwmPager: Window3DBorders
*FvwmPager: MiniIcons
*FvwmPager: DeskHilight
Style FvwmPager !Title, !Borders, StaysOnBottom, Sticky

# FvwmEvent
#
# FvwmEvent is a module that can run an action or function
# on specific events. This instance changes which desk number
# is highlighted when the desk is changed.
DestroyModuleConfig EventNewDesk:*
*EventNewDesk: PassID
*EventNewDesk: new_desk ChangeDesk

# FvwmForm
#
# FvwmForm is a module that can be used to build a GUI
# form. Used with fvwm-menu-desktop-config.fpl.
# This sets the default colorsets.
*FvwmFormDefault: Colorset 10
*FvwmFormDefault: ItemColorset 13

## Set The Thumbnail Cache Folder
SetEnv cache $[HOME]/.fvwm/cache/
## Set The Scripts Folder
SetEnv scripts $[HOME]/.fvwm/scripts

## To Create a Thumbnail on Minimize
# Call the script to create a thumbnail using ImageMagick & xwd
DestroyFunc Thumbnail
AddToFunc Thumbnail
+ I ThisWindow (Shaded) WindowShade
+ I PipeRead 'bash $[scripts]/crthumb "$[w.id]" "$[cache]"'
# Restore the window
DestroyFunc DeThumbnail
AddToFunc DeThumbnail
+ I PipeRead 'bash $[scripts]/dethumb "$[w.id]" "$[cache]"'
*FvwmEvent: deiconify DeThumbnail

## Minimize to Thumbnail Placeholder
Style * IconBox 400x600-20+48, IconGrid 1 4, \
IconFill top right, !IconTitle, IconBackgroundRelief 0

# redefine to not warp the cursor
DestroyFunc WindowListFunc
AddToFunc WindowListFunc
+ I Iconify off
+ I FlipFocus
+ I Raise

# # Qillqaq
# Style "*" HilightFore #e5e6e6, HilightBack #1e1e1e
# Style "*" Color #adadad #1e1e1e
